➜链圈层，创场景 重庆融创文旅城供应8天不重样欢乐体验，其背后秘密是什么？
http://www.sohu.com/a/423285867_563335	42787
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>这个双节</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>去哪里能</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;">get</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>到</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;">8</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>天不重样的欢乐游玩体验</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>？</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>这道题</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>重庆融创文旅城可以给出满分答案</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>。</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>重庆融创文旅城开业即</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>创高峰</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>开业首个周末</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>（</span>9 </span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>月</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;">26</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>日</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>、</span>27 </span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>日</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>）</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>共计接待客流突破</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;">40</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>万人次</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>国庆</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>假日</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>期间</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>游客游玩热度继续递增</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>成为不少重庆及周边地区家庭旅游的首选之地</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>。</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>目前</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>重庆</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>融创文旅</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>日嗨夜闹的欢乐体验还在</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>持续</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>供应中</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>作为全国</span>12 <span>座融创文旅城中业态布局最多的项目，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>在这里</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>不同人群都能找到适合自己的专属欢乐体验</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>。</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>渝乐小镇里人头攒动</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>无数情侣、家人、朋友结伴而来</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>尽兴而归</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>；</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>在融创茂里</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>礼献国庆的优惠折扣激活无限的购物潜力</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>；</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>水世界</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>、</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>海世界</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>、</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>雪世界里人潮涌动</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>欢声笑语不断</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>；日落舞台下沉式广场</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>日日嗨歌劲舞不断</span>…… </span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>一站式满足</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>不同圈层</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>、不同家庭微度假需求，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>重庆融创文旅城名不虚传</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>开放式经营满足多圈层人群</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>欢乐需求</span></span></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>在当下全国文旅城都经历了同质化运营而带来客流量不断下降的阵痛时</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>重庆融创文旅城承接融创文旅从设计到内容、服务的运营能力，推出</span>“开放式 <span>-</span><span>无需大门票免费入园”的经营战略，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>这一经营模式促进了更多欢乐场景的发生和共建，引领了文旅转型新趋势。</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>这样的模式获得了游客的一致好评</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;">“过去的游乐园一家人光门票动辄就上千元</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>但是现在，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>一家人都能在这里找到想玩可玩的</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>这种具有自由感的消费方式让人觉得很舒适</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>。</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;">”专程从涪陵带一家人来重庆度假的宋先生说</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201008/237e457e61a64c1c9e4829deb8652701.png" /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>据了解，重庆融创文旅城根据游客</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>实际需求</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>推出单项票、组合票和通票，园内机动游乐项目单项单次收费在</span>10 <span>元至</span><span>50</span><span>元不等，多种票价模式可满足不同人群的游玩需求。</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>在国庆期间</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>重庆融创文旅城</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>进一步串联起其他行业的品牌商、合作伙伴，创造出多维的消费空间和欢乐场景，延伸出更多欢乐体验。</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>例如</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>十一期间</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，百事可乐西南品牌馆</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>在</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>融创</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>渝乐小镇火热开馆</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>馆内陈列着可供游客打卡拍照的艺术装置</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>随意凹造型出片率都非常高</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>深受年轻群体和抖音网红达人的喜爱</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">“开放式经营”还体现在链接更多圈层文化</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>多元文化在这里聚集</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>一座</span>“山城潮流新主场”呼之欲出 </span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>。</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>据介绍</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，《这！就是街舞</span>3 <span>》西南挑战赛</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>将于</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;">10</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>月</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;">4</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>日至</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;">7</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>日在融创渝乐小镇内火热开赛</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，来自各地的潮酷</span>dancer </span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>秀舞技</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，王炸</span>MC </span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>毛毛</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>、</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>车车</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>最潮</span>DJ LEEGO <span>、</span><span>2-</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;">Gunz</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>街舞</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>明星舞者</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>陈妍臻</span>Nikki </span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>、</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>穆童</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>、</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>王润等</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>也</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>将来到现场点燃这场金秋最强赛事</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>。</span></span></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
